\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b1 Chapter 8: The Collaboration}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Haruhi found Nagano in the music room, strumming his guitar with a faraway look in his eyes. She cleared her throat, and he glanced up, surprised to see her.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Hey,\u8221\'94 she said, trying to sound casual. \u8220\'93I was thinking\u8230\'85 if you\u8217\'92re going to perform at the festival, you\u8217\'92ll need a really good song, right?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Nagano shrugged. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I guess. But I\u8217\'92m not exactly a poet.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93That\u8217\'92s where Honoka comes in,\u8221\'94 Haruhi said, grinning. \u8220\'93She\u8217\'92s an amazing writer. I bet she could help you with the lyrics.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Nagano\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s eyes widened. \u8220\'93Honoka Aoki? The class ace? Why would she want to help me?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Because she\u8217\'92s nice,\u8221\'94 Haruhi said, rolling her eyes. \u8220\'93And because I asked her. She said yes, by the way.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Nagano looked skeptical but didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t argue. \u8220\'93Fine. But if she hates my music, don\u8217\'92t blame me.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Later that day, Haruhi brought Honoka to the music room. Nagano was already there, tuning his guitar. He looked up when they entered, and for a moment, no one spoke.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Uh, hi,\u8221\'94 Nagano said awkwardly.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Hello,\u8221\'94 Honoka replied, equally stiff.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Haruhi clapped her hands, breaking the tension. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Okay, you two! Let\u8217\'92s make some music.\u8221\'94}
